    }

}
```

## Additional Information

No additional changes are required in the `pom.xml` file for this update. However, make sure that the `hibernate-orm` dependency is updated to version 6.0 or later, which is the version used by Quarkus.

Also, note that the `allocationSize` attribute is set to 1 in the updated code. This means that the sequence value will be incremented by 1 each time a new value is requested. You can adjust this value according to your requirements.
